472
00:24:45,980 --> 00:24:47,940
Juanita came to our
house last week.

473
00:24:48,070 --> 00:24:50,439
Oh, right. Thanks for coming.

474
00:24:50,440 --> 00:24:51,420
Of course.

475
00:24:51,730 --> 00:24:52,720
Mom.

476
00:24:53,890 --> 00:24:55,889
