Do you want me to heat it up?

504
00:26:16,850 --> 00:26:18,130
No. It's okay.

505
00:26:19,680 --> 00:26:20,620
Mm!

506
00:26:21,410 --> 00:26:22,369
Aah!

507
00:26:22,370 --> 00:26:25,599
It's... it's... it's boiling!
